name: GlobalClashResolutionStrategy
shortdesc: The resolution strategy to employ for imported styles that have the same names as existing styles.

property.name: LOAD_ALL_WITH_OVERWRITE
property.shortdesc: Overwrites existing styles whose names clash with imported items.

property.name: LOAD_ALL_WITH_RENAME
property.shortdesc: Renames imported styles whose names clash with existing items to preserve existing items.

property.name: DO_NOT_LOAD_THE_STYLE
property.shortdesc: Does not import styles whose names clash with existing items.
